<doc id="1120290" wikidata="Q1806732" url="?curid=1120290" title="Sooretama">
<text>Sooretama is a municipality located in the Brazilian state of Espírito Santo. Its population was 30,680 (2020) and its area is .

The municipality contains part of the Sooretama Biological Reserve, a strictly protected conservation unit created in 1982 when two earlier units were merged.

==See also==
*List of municipalities in Espírito Santo

